        <h1>Energy</h1>
        <p>Clean&#039;s Energy programs help people save money and improve the environment by making energy choices  -- sometimes all this takes are small changes at an individual level to generate a positive impact on a large scale.  <br />
<br />
To date, Clean has helped reduce energy use in Nova Scotia by over 160 gigawatt hours (GWh). To help put that number in perspective, it&#039;s the equivalent of removing the annual energy consumption of over 14,500 homes from Nova Scotia&#039;s electricity grid!</p>
