              <div class="feature-block first">
        <h1>HomeWarming</h1>
        <div class="block-body">
          <p>HomeWarming helps eligible Nova Scotians save money on heating bills and feel more comfortable year-round through free efficiency upgrades.</p>

          <a href="http://clean.ns.ca/programs/energy/homewarming-low-income-homeowner-energy-upgrades/">Enjoy a warmer home, and a happier wallet</a>
        </div>
      </div>
              <div class="feature-block second">
        <h1>The Atlantic Stormwater Initiative</h1>
        <div class="block-body">
          <p>Our Atlantic Stormwater Initiative is a region-wide project that aims to support climate change adaptation by reducing the negative impacts of stormwater runoff.</p>

          <a href="http://clean.ns.ca/programs/water/atlantic-stormwater/">Find out why we're not going with the flow</a>
        </div>
      </div>
              <div class="feature-block third">
        <h1>Contact us</h1>
        <div class="block-body">
          <p>Toll-free: 1-855-736-3474<br />
Halifax region: (902) 420-3474<br />
Facebook.com/CleanFoundation<br />
Twitter.com/CleanFoundation</p>

          <a href="/contact">Clean is a call or click away</a>
        </div>
